==English==
===Etymology===
From [[Greek]] [[πατριωτικός]] (''patriotikos'').

===Adjective===

'''patriotic'''

#Inspired by patriotism; actuated by love of one's country; zealously and unselfishly devoted to the service of one's country; as, a patriotic statesman, vigilance.

